{"tid":324927,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"謝偉俊：議事規則應改 不應因議員出缺加快","createTime":"2017-07-16T23:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T02:22:58.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45bdfacabdccf96a1a9957655ca9171e83d5338e","tid":324927,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T23:06:07.000Z","msg":"謝偉俊：議事規則應改 不應因議員出缺加快<br />\n謝偉俊承認委員會內「很多人都不想改嘢」，而建制派很多人亦認為在修改議事規則一事上，是「不改好過改」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170717/s00002/1500228744593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170717%2Fs00002%2F1500228744593&d=pGABYCmRHTumhql11H3vy2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=8308bc9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170717%2Fs00002%2F1500228744593&h=71178c61\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170717/s00002/1500228744593</a>"},{"pid":"17680e4d656446365f7ef4bdbdb6cb61f4a7c1dc","tid":324927,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T23:08:43.000Z","msg":"補選完先修改也唔遲"},{"pid":"fb9f5ae4fc55f44bf328f1a374c09902af1e07b9","tid":324927,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T23:12:09.000Z","msg":"【DQ四議員】非建制派補選至少失2席 失分組點票否決權<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170714/large/1500036785_71a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170714%2Flarge%2F1500036785_71a6.png&h=77328a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼青年新政梁頌恆及游蕙禎被政府褫奪立法會議員資格後，法庭再裁定政府司法覆核勝訴，認為羅冠聰、劉小麗、梁國雄及姚松炎的宣誓不合規格，宣佈由去年10月12日宣誓當日起計，4人議席失效，若上訴失敗，便有6席要補選。科大社會學部副教授成名預計，建制派在九西及新東應最少奪2席，地區直選議席將增至18席，相反非建制派會減至17席，喪失在分組點票時的否決權。<br />\n<br />\n他分析，在九西及新東的兩大選區，建制派必然會派人參選，即使泛民派代表出戰補選，在比例代表制下，估計建制派會在九西及新東取得最少2席。而只有1席出缺的港島區，將按單議席單票制補選，估計對非建制派有利。<br />\n<br />\n至於非建制派能否有策略可全奪回6席，他稱，「我覺得係悲觀」，因在比例代表制下，建制派有一定核心的支持者，即鐵票，認為非建制派「無可能6席贏返晒返來」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56957050&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56957050%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170714&d=pGABYCmRHTumhql11H3vy2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=cda98178\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56957050%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170714&h=5dd843a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56957050&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170714</a>"},{"pid":"e414cd6f4557a9f594a168913e310d60c12e2726","tid":324927,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T23:19:20.000Z","msg":"而家都隨時剪得<br />\n無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e034baaa08774037a1be33296018dd48c41ed54","tid":324927,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T23:21:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家都隨時剪得<br />\n無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔LIKE咪DQ"},{"pid":"76a20014b43b3b4c54d58755de6c9323fd16b500","tid":324927,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cdd16098556687744602babbb1b499c6a85899a","tid":324927,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家都隨時剪得<br />\n無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣啱，只要搵個唔要臉主席就可以剪布<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}